	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pugnatum est in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> 19. decembris a 10. hora antemeridiana usque in multam noctem.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utra pars victoriam assequta sit, variant sententiae.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Capitanei Helvetici superstites gloriantur literis ad magistratum suum scriptis se vicisse et omnia fecisse; <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538">rex Carolus</persName> ad magistratum Helveticum literis idem testatur; interim fatentur acerrime esse pugnatum: <foreign xml:lang="de">sy habind uff der walstat 21 houptlüt und fendrych gelassen; die schwartzen rüter syend inen 3 mal duch die ordnung geritten;</foreign> inde reliqua aestimare licet.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentina</placeName> scribitur 2. ianuarii vicisse Condensem, admirallium et <persName type="auto_name">Dandelottum</persName> captivos, inprimis avunculum conestabilem captivum duxisse Aureliam; exercitum Condensem occupatum in diripiendis castris; ibi ex insperato irruisse <persName type="citizen_name">Guysium</persName> cum equitibus acribus et caepisse Condensem et duxisse <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378" cert="high">Lutetiam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex utraque parte quae scribuntur, in hoc conveniunt: cecidisse mareschalchum <persName type="auto_name">S. Andreae</persName>, seniorem f[ilium] conestablii, grandem priorem <placeName type="citizen_name">Franciae</placeName>, <persName type="citizen_name">Guysii</persName> fratrem: multos captos, multos esse saucios, imprimis Domalam, <persName type="citizen_name">Guysii</persName> fratrem.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name">Angli</placeName> non interfuere pugnae.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">10000 ascendere scribuntur <persName type="auto_name">Aurelium</persName>, ubi colligitur, quod reliquum est evangelicorum.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Guysius</persName> et sui triumphant; alii putant illos frustra triumphare.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Multa sunt, quae scribere possem; sed mira varietas prohibet, ne scribam omnia; <foreign xml:lang="de">die zyt wirts bringen.</foreign></s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oremus dominum.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluto sororem et <persName type="auto_name">Ulmios</persName>, nepotes ex sorore etc.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Festinantissime scripsi.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale aeternum.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Maximilianus</persName> est <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustae</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aiunt <persName ref="p458" cert="high">Brentium</persName> mortuum; ego non credo, vellem tamen me scire certo; scribunt <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> esse mortuum.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam esset mortuus, antequam scripsisset <persName type="auto_name">Eutychianum</persName> librum suum De maiestate etc., cui iam respondi per dei gratiam!</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ora pro nobis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ianuarii 8. 1563.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta fratrem tuum etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus ille <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">B[ullingerus]</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName>, singulari suo amico, fratri charissimo et domino colendissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="de" type="manual">An m. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosien Blaureren</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Vermerk von <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">A. Blarers</persName> Hand:]</note>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Conflictus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallicus</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
